PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FWords by Sanjay Jha, ITV News in New
OL,8,FDelhi
OL,10,FIndia has begun the first phase of
OL,11,Fwhat has been described as the world's
OL,12,Flargest population census ever
OL,13,Fundertaken.
OL,15,FThe census will prove to be massive
OL,16,Fexercise in governance which will seek
OL,17,Fto enumerate more than 1.4 billion
OL,18,Fpeople, using digital tools for the
OL,19,Ffirst time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FWhile the Indian census, conducted
OL,8,Fonce a decade, has been likened to a
OL,9,Fnational election in scale, the
OL,10,Fupcoming Census 2027 marks a major
OL,11,Fchange, with Indian authorities
OL,12,Fadopting digital tools.
OL,14,FThose tools will include mobile
OL,15,Fapplications and real-time monitoring,
OL,16,Fto conduct the massive exercise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FMore than three million enumerators -
OL,8,Froughly the same size as the entire
OL,9,Fpopulation of Armenia - will survey
OL,10,FIndia's vast terrain, which comprises
OL,11,Fsome of the world's largest cities,
OL,12,Fmost extreme deserts, highest mountain
OL,13,Franges, tropical islands, and remotest
OL,14,Fforests.
OL,16,FBut, how will the census work, and why
OL,17,Fdoes it matter? ITV News explains.
OL,19,FDigital-first approach
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FUnlike previous censuses, enumerators
OL,8,Fthis time around will use a dedicated
OL,9,Fmobile application to collect data,
OL,10,Frather than traditional paper
OL,11,Fquestionnaires.
OL,13,FIndian authorities say this will help
OL,14,Freduce errors, increase efficiency,
OL,15,Fand speed up data processing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FHouseholds will also be allowed to
OL,8,Ffill out questionnaires through a
OL,9,Fdedicated self-enumeration web portal,
OL,10,Fwhich will be available in 16
OL,11,Flanguages, allowing some households to
OL,12,Ffill out their questionnaires before
OL,13,Fenumerators visit their homes to
OL,14,Fverify the information.
OL,16,FThis, Indian authorities say, will
OL,17,Fallow households, some of whom do not
OL,18,Fhave internet connectivity, to benefit
OL,19,Ffrom the use of digital tools and
OL,20,Ftraditional door-to-door enumeration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FParticipants who complete this process
OL,8,Fwill be issued a unique identification
OL,9,Fnumber to be shared with interviewers
OL,10,Fduring subsequent visits.
OL,12,FTwo Phases of Data Collection
OL,14,FThe census will be carried out in two
OL,15,Fphases.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe first phase will cover data
OL,8,Fcollection on housing conditions and
OL,9,Fhousehold amenities. In this phase,
OL,10,Fdata will be collected on housing
OL,11,Fconditions, water and sanitation
OL,12,Ffacilities, cooking fuels, and
OL,13,Fhousehold assets.
OL,15,FThe second phase, scheduled for early
OL,16,F2027, will be dedicated to data
OL,17,Fcollection on the size of the
OL,18,Fpopulation, as well as data on
OL,19,Fdemographics and socio-economic
OL,20,Finformation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FIt is confirmed that caste data will
OL,8,Fbe collected during this exercise, a
OL,9,Fcrucial aspect considering its
OL,10,Fpolitical implications in Indian
OL,11,Fsociety.
OL,13,FThe official reference date for the
OL,14,FIndian census is fixed for March 1,
OL,15,F2027. However, for areas affected by
OL,16,Fsnowfall in the Himalayas, separate
OL,17,Fdata collection schedules will be
OL,18,Ffollowed.
OL,20,FFirst Indian Census in over a decade
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FCensus 2027 will be India's first
OL,8,Fcensus in over a decade. The previous
OL,9,Fcensus, in 2021, was postponed.
OL,11,FThis will be the 16th Indian census
OL,12,Fand the eighth since Indian
OL,13,Findependence in 1947.
OL,15,FThis exercise comes at a crucial point
OL,16,Fin Indian history, where policymakers,
OL,17,Fresearchers, and businesses have been
OL,18,Fforced to rely on outdated data for
OL,19,Fover a decade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FIt is reported that this exercise will
OL,8,Foffer an update on how India has
OL,9,Fchanged since the pandemic and over
OL,10,Fthe years of rapid economic and social
OL,11,Fchanges.
OL,13,FA massive logistical exercise
OL,15,FThe government has also allocated an
OL,16,Fapproximate 117 billion (around $1.4
OL,17,Fbillion) for the census, including
OL,18,Fdigital infrastructure, training,
OL,19,Flogistics, and payment for census
OL,20,Fworkers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe preparations also include a
OL,8,Fnationwide trial for digital
OL,9,Ftechnology across thousands of census
OL,10,Fblocks, and a multi-layered training
OL,11,Fprogram that includes national
OL,12,Ftrainers, master trainers, and
OL,13,Finstructors at the ground level.
OL,15,FAltogether, tens of thousands of
OL,16,Ftraining sessions are anticipated to
OL,17,Fprepare the millions of workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe training content is also available
OL,8,Fin multiple regional languages to
OL,9,Fprevent errors, as the country has
OL,10,Fhundreds of languages and dialects.
OL,12,FData security and oversight
OL,14,FIn addition to the introduction of
OL,15,Fdigital technology for census
OL,16,Fcollection, new measures have also
OL,17,Fbeen put in place to ensure the
OL,18,Fsecurity and protection of
OL,19,Findividuals' information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThe new measures include secure
OL,8,Fstorage, controlled access, and real-
OL,9,Ftime monitoring of census operations.
OL,11,FThe authorities have also clarified
OL,12,Fthat the use of digital technology for
OL,13,Fthe census is still a voluntary
OL,14,Fprocess, and that traditional methods
OL,15,Fare still available to ensure that no
OL,16,Fone is left out.
OL,18,FThe administrative boundaries across
OL,19,Fthe country are also locked until the
OL,20,Fcensus is completed to ensure
OL,21,Fconsistency and future comparison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
