FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FWhy the census matters
OL,14,FApart from just measuring the number
OL,15,Fof people, the census plays a major
OL,16,Frole in the formation of public
OL,17,Fpolicies for the country.
OL,19,FThe numbers help to determine the
OL,20,Fallocation of government funds and
OL,21,Fwelfare measures for the people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FThey help economists, urban planners,
OL,8,Fand health experts to get a clearer
OL,9,Funderstanding of the country and its
OL,10,Fdevelopment.
OL,12,FCounting a nation of continental scale
OL,14,FDespite all the technology, the census
OL,15,Fis still a human exercise, and its
OL,16,Fsuccess depends on millions of
OL,17,Ftemporary employees who ensure that no
OL,18,Fone is left out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775059859
OL,3,CIndia launches world's largest census
OL,4,Caiming to count more than a billion
OL,5,Cpeople
OL,7,FIf the digital census is a success,
OL,8,Fthen it would be an example for other
OL,9,Fcountries to learn from, especially
OL,10,Fthose as large and diverse as India.
OL,12,FFor now, the exercise is a rare
OL,13,Fattempt to measure a country that is
OL,14,Fof continental scale, not just through
OL,15,Fforms and questionnaires, but also
OL,16,Fthrough technology and networks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
